        a                        fabio:Figure ;
        dc:description           "Figures 5 - 6. Holotype of Epicoela seminigra Diaz Female. 5 Antenna 6 Scutellar plate (dorsal view)." , "Figures 1 - 4. Holotype of Euxestophaga argentinensis Gallardo sp. n. Female. 1 Habitus (lateral view) 2 Head and mesosoma (dorsal view), arrow indicates posterior margin of gena distinct, but not carinata 3 Head (posterior view) and mesosoma (dorsal view), arrow indicates basal margin of forewing lacking hair fringe. Male 4 Antenna, arrow indicates posterior margin of scutellum bluntly rounded." ;
        fabio:hasRepresentation  "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/124109" , "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/124108" .

